{"tid":157811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"納DEE終於比人拉左","createTime":"2017-03-15T19:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T19:44:24.000Z","uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"000bb763fa0f0a827f1e257dde035fa6504665a9","tid":157811,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T19:38:04.000Z","msg":"昨午1時許，屯門友愛邨一單位，一對38歲及32歲南亞夫婦，因瑣事發生爭執，身上有酒氣丈的夫，以掃帚及鞋襲擊妻子，並以言語恐嚇。警員接報到場，妻子清醒送屯門醫院治理。經初步調查，案件列刑事恐嚇及襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，丈夫涉案被捕。案件交屯門警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170316/56434460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170316%2F56434460&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9f05fb7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170316%2F56434460&h=2304d62b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170316/56434460</a>"},{"pid":"19ba4c8d398c5404fb8e9a0c68af3f95f9ddf075","tid":157811,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T19:44:24.000Z","msg":"納dee撚係南亞狗<br />\n咪亂up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}